h][av_cell_one_fourth vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'0px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#61989b\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' link_hover=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-8tvfuf\']\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_fourth][av_cell_one_fourth vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'0px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#30e8d5\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' link_hover=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-8mmm6n\']\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_fourth][av_cell_one_fourth vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'0px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#b6e7e3\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' link_hover=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-8h4p6n\']\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_fourth][/av_layout_row][av_layout_row border=\'\' min_height=\'0\' color=\'main_color\' mobile=\'av-flex-cells\' id=\'hello\' av_uid=\'av-8fmr1z\']\r\n\r\n[av_cell_one_half vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'100px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background_color=\'\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-88j09j\']\r\n\r\n[av_heading heading=\'Meet <u> Lisa</u>\' tag=\'h1\' link_apply=\'\' link=\'manually,http://\' link_target=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' size=\'70\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' margin=\'\' margin_sync=\'true\' padding=\'30\' color=\'\' custom_font=\'\' av-medium-font-size-title=\'\' av-small-font-size-title=\'\' av-mini-font-size-title=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-jrxe28rq\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'22\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-7usk3z\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Overwhelmed and stressed out with little self-care, Lisa had her wake-up call when she turned 40 years old. Tired of going through the motions of life with her lifestyle and career, she decided to pursue her passion of helping women attain optimal and vibrant health and bring more happiness and self confidence into their lives. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Through her coaching and trainings, she’s here to teach you how to create a life you love with simplicity and ease. She specializes in helping others design a life that allows them more time doing what they love. She is the host of The Therapy Show with Lisa Mustard and Your Best (Mid) Life with Lisa Mustard. She is the creator of Your Brand Buildr, a free app to help you build your personal brand on social media. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is married to Billy and they have two daughters. They inspire her to live her best life every day.</span>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_half][av_cell_one_half vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'550px,100px,550px,100px\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#b6e7e3\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'http://handspeak.web-art.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2-1.jpg\' attachment=\'510\' attachment_size=\'full\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'center right\' background_repeat=\'stretch\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' link_hover=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-7by8cv\']\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_half][/av_layout_row][av_three_fourth first min_height=\'\' vertical_alignment=\'\' space=\'\' custom_margin=\'\' margin=\'0px\' padding=\'0px\' border=\'\' border_color=\'\' radius=\'0px\' background_color=\'\' src=\'\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' animation=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-130bnz\']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'20\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-ppb2f\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-524 size-medium\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" src=\"http://handspeak.web-art.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/logo-1-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><b>What is Your Brand Buildr?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your Brand Buildr is an app designed to help you create valuable content and get you on a consistent schedule of sharing as much (or as little) as you like on your social media platforms. YBB is for those who want to create a solid, authentic and congruent brand that has people knowing, liking and trusting you within a matter of weeks or months.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Over the years, Lisa has spent countless hours learning from on line business mentors and coaches. The one thing every coach teaches and preaches is CONSISTENCY of daily actions when it comes to building your online brand. And there\'s never been an easier way to build your brand than through social media platforms. Your Brand Buildr teaches you how to get consistent and reminds you when it\'s time to post. </span>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_three_fourth]'),
