-8pxxpj\']\n\n[/av_cell_one_fourth][av_cell_one_fourth vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'0px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#c9e8e2\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' link_hover=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-8k4xsf\']\n\n[/av_cell_one_fourth][/av_layout_row][av_layout_row border=\'\' min_height=\'0\' color=\'main_color\' mobile=\'av-flex-cells\' id=\'hello\' av_uid=\'av-8dx2dj\']\n\n[av_cell_one_half vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'100px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background_color=\'\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'top left\' background_repeat=\'no-repeat\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-89g9sn\']\n\n[av_heading heading=\'Meet <u>Lisa</u> \' tag=\'h1\' link_apply=\'\' link=\'manually,http://\' link_target=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote\' size=\'70\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' margin=\'\' margin_sync=\'true\' padding=\'30\' color=\'\' custom_font=\'\' av-medium-font-size-title=\'\' av-small-font-size-title=\'\' av-mini-font-size-title=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-jrti5qov\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]\n\n[av_textblock size=\'24\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-7uxm7j\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Overwhelmed and stressed out with little self-care, Lisa had her wake-up call when she turned 40 years old. Tired of going through the motions of life with her lifestyle and career, she decided to pursue her passion of helping women attain optimal and vibrant health and bring more happiness and self confidence into their lives. </span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Through her coaching and trainings, she’s here to teach you how to create a life you love with simplicity and ease. She specializes in helping others design a life that allows them more time doing what they love. She is the host of The Therapy Show with Lisa Mustard and Your Best (Mid) Life with Lisa Mustard. She is the creator of Your Brand Buildr, a free app to help you build your personal brand on social media. </span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is married to Billy and they have two daughters. They inspire her to live her best life every day.</span>\n[/av_textblock]\n\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'20\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_margin_top=\'30px\' custom_margin_bottom=\'30px\' icon_select=\'yes\' custom_icon_color=\'\' icon=\'ue808\' font=\'entypo-fontello\' av_uid=\'av-7oyns7\']\n\n[/av_cell_one_half][av_cell_one_half vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'550px,100px,550px,100px\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#b6e7e3\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'http://handspeak.web-art.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2.jpg\' attachment=\'434\' attachment_size=\'full\' background_attachment=\'scroll\' background_position=\'center right\' background_repeat=\'stretch\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'\' link_hover=\'\' mobile_display=\'\' av_uid=\'av-qr1v3\']\n\n[/av_cell_one_half][/av_layout_row][av_layout_row border=\'\' min_height=\'15px\' color=\'main_color\' mobile=\'av-fixed-cells\' id=\'welcome\' av_uid=\'av-96r9dj\']\n\n[av_cell_one_fourth vertical_align=\'top\' padding=\'0px\' padding_sync=\'true\' background=\'bg_color\' background_color=\'#4ce8d5\' background_gradient_color1=\'\' background_gradient_color2=\'\' background_gradient_direction=\'vertical\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' background_attachment