ght=\'\' animation=\'no-animation\' av_uid=\'av-jruwcqy7\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_image]\n\n[av_textblock size=\'18\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-66yh4l\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\nFeel free to check out my Facebook and Instagram pages as another way to see how I connect virtually with my personal market to share our pieces! You can find me on my social media sites below. I also do pop-up fitness and wellness events in the Columbia, SC area.\n[/av_textblock]\n\n[av_heading heading=\' <u>What makes</u> our brand and pieces so unique and special? \' tag=\'h2\' link_apply=\'\' link=\'manually,http://\' link_target=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote modern-centered\' size=\'42\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' margin=\'\' margin_sync=\'true\' padding=\'30\' color=\'\' custom_font=\'\' av-medium-font-size-title=\'\' av-small-font-size-title=\'\' av-mini-font-size-title=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-jruw1in4\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]\n\n[av_video src=\'https://youtu.be/1W7eUppISRQ\' mobile_image=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' format=\'16-9\' width=\'16\' height=\'9\' conditional_play=\'\' av_uid=\'av-jruw4cej\']\n\n[av_textblock size=\'18\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-66yh4l\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\nCheck out these review videos covering some of our most popular legging and bra styles to get a feel for how amazing they are!\n\nNothing is more motivating for an active and healthy lifestyle than feeling great in your favorite activewear and we have pieces designed thoughtfully for all shapes, sizes, ages, and activity levels! Your friends, family, and daily social connections will be thrilled to discover this fantastic brand and all that it offers them as well!\n\nYou cannot beat the versatility, fit, and function of ZYIA Active while still maintaining an affordable and attainable price point.\n\nZYIA maintains more of a \"boutique\" type shopping experience as it releases new pieces almost every week! This unique business model offers continued excitement and engagement for both you as the representative, as well as your clients who want to keep their athletic and athleisure wardrobe fresh and fun!\n[/av_textblock]\n\n[av_video src=\'https://youtu.be/oqT8el-JSX8\' mobile_image=\'\' attachment=\'\' attachment_size=\'\' format=\'16-9\' width=\'16\' height=\'9\' conditional_play=\'\' av_uid=\'av-jruw4cej\']\n\n[av_textblock size=\'18\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-66yh4l\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\nInterested in learning more about the amazing compensation plan and perks of being a ZYIA Active Representative??\n\nRemember you don\'t have to be a sales or business expert, or have previous experience to be super successful! I will be your personal mentor to help you make a business and marketing plan that fits into your lifestyle organically. Just a little hustle and heart is all it takes to turn this incredible opportunity into something AMAZING!\n[/av_textblock]\n\n[av_heading heading=\' <u>ZYIA ACTIVE </u> COMPENSATION\' tag=\'h2\' link_apply=\'\' link=\'manually,http://\' link_target=\'\' style=\'blockquote modern-quote modern-centered\' size=\'42\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' margin=\'\' margin_sync=\'true\' padding=\'30\' color=\'\' custom_font=\'\' av-medium-font-size-title=\'\' av-small-font-size-title=\'\' av-mini-font-size-title=\'\' av-medium-font-size=\'\' av-small-font-size=\'\' av-mini-font-size=\'\' av_uid=\'av-jruw1in4\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]\n\n[av_image src=\'http://handspeak.web-art.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/image3.png\' attachment=\'476\' attachment_size=\'full\' align=\'center\' styling=\'\' hover=\'\' link=\'\' target=\'\' caption=\'\' font