(421, 1, '2019-02-06 15:32:37', '2019-02-06 15:32:37', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ok, what does this have to do with social media and personal branding? A lot.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ever have one of those days where you don\'t FEEL like touching your business? Or creating posts? Perhaps you feel frustrated that you\'re putting all this time into your business and brand and you aren\'t seeing the fruits of your labor show up in your bank account yet? And then do you head over to private messenger and start talking with another gal who you know feels the same? You start to commiserate over how hard it is..how you\'re hearing so many nos..how if you only had x,y, or z things would be different in your business?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'m here to tell you I\'ve been there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I had days like that. In fact, I still have them. But I know how to shift my energy (and actions!)&nbsp;these days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When my energy is low, my mood is low, my enthusiasm is low, my connections are low...see where I\'m going with this? And it\'s easy to stay in this trajectory if we don\'t make an effort and take inspired actions to get out of it!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So how do you get out of this funk? How do bring more positive energy to your life, your brand, your business?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here\'s what I\'ve been doing the past few weeks and all these tips are helping me bring more positive energy to my day:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Morning meditation. First thing. No checking Facebook (this is hard for me!) It does set the tone for the morning and I\'m loving it! I\'m working towards full on meditation on my own. However, in the meantime, I\'m using guided meditations and I am loving this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UZs5Q9-tNv4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">one</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. Music. I just made my first Spotify playlist. Why did I wait so long? If you\'d like to hear my Up Your Vibe list, click&nbsp;<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/user/4vztw1ap8rlq0m60bpsza5ths/playlist/4RrdkxVf9jnnssADbYP5aA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>. Music really helps me connect back to my spirit and energy.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Movement. It can be anything. Some days I\'m able to head to the gym. Some days I workout at home. Some days I get 10 mins of stretching and yoga done. Some days I walk and listen to my playlist.&nbsp;But MOVING helps get my energy flowing and releases a ton of endorphins.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. Oils. I was a skeptic. However, I notice a shift in my energy within a few minutes of starting my diffuser. Who knew? I\'m glad I gave them a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lisamustard.isagenix.com/en-us/products/essence\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">try&nbsp;</a>as I have been running my diffuser non-stop for over a week now.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. Taking breaks. I\'ve been getting up, out of my work chair and going outside and walking around the block. The fresh air and movement (even though it\'s still hot as you know what here in South Carolina!) lifts my mood and energy pretty quickly.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So where\'s the proof all these actions are helping me in my business? I feel more aligned with my&nbsp;brand. Which in turn helps me create value-adding content. Which leads to more meaningful connections and relationships. I feel more energized for my work. I also feel more present for my family. Working on my energy (and remember, we attract who and what we are!) has been amazing.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here\'s to upping your vibe and bringing the energy to your day!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I hope you found this helpful! Have you grabbed your copy of My Branding Must Knows for Increasing Your Visibility on Facebook? If not, you can get it&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/7secretssocialmediamakeover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to Bring the Energy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-bring-the-energy', '', '', '2019-02-18 17:16:17', '2019-02-18 17:16:17', '', 0, 'http://handspeak.web-art.net/?p=421', 0, 'post', '', 0),
