(481, 1, '2019-02-06 19:35:34', '2019-02-06 19:35:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content is key to building your personal brand. Yet, so many people tell me they struggle with creating it! I truly understand&nbsp;though because a few years ago I would sit for hours and work on posts, videos and topics for blogging. I ended up a teary mess because I had no clue what to share! I have many interests and tons of knowledge however, it was hard for me to get it out of my brain and into social media.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Looking back, I know why. I hadn\'t defined my niche. I was trying to market to anyone and everyone who would come across my social media accounts. When I finally realized I had to niche it down, things began to come together and content creation became a breeze!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First things first. Who is your target audience? (Please don\'t say ANYONE who loves ____! This will only have you pulling out you hair and leave you frustrated and stuck in moving forward in building your brand.) What are their struggles? What solutions can you provide for them? What value can you offer them?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Next, once you know who you are marketing to, content is easy. Like, too easy, in my opinion. Let\'s use the example of health and wellness. My niche is women, 30+, who want to feel amazing in their skin, rock their self confidence, attain optimal and vibrant health and create a life that allows them more time with their families. So every time I create a piece of content, I am thinking about these women and how I can help them.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where do I find content? I keep my eyes open to topics that would be of interest to my niche. Seriously, health and wellness is a billion dollar industry and pretty much every where I go, there\'s information out there. When I\'m at the grocery store, checking out, I see&nbsp;magazine titles. When I\'m on Facebook, I see people posting about their issues. And one of my favorite places is the internet. I will google a few key words and boom! INSTANT IDEAS and CONTENT!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content creation isn\'t rocket science. It\'s being aware of the trends. It\'s knowing your audience. It\'s adding value with help, support and ideas. Remember, not everyone is in your niche. Not everyone is interested in what you have to offer. And that is 100% ok! Don\'t worry about them. Instead, start calling out your tribe and creating raving fans of your content,,then the sky\'s the limit on the impact you will make!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Receive my free gift - 8 Must Knows for Personal Branding&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/7secretssocialmediamakeover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">HERE</a>!</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Struggling to determine your personal brand? I know the feeling! After almost 2 years of studying and building my own brand, I offer one on one coaching. See if we\'re a good fit by filling out this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/H8MK97J\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>form</strong></a><a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></a>and I\'ll be in touch with you soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Content Creation Made Simple', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '411-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-06 19:35:34', '2019-02-06 19:35:34', '', 411, 'http://handspeak.web-art.net/411-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(482, 1, '2019-02-06 19:36:05', '2019-02-06 19:36:05', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content is key to building your personal brand. Yet, so many people tell me they struggle with creating it! I truly understand&nbsp;though because a few years ago I would sit for hours and work on posts, videos and topics for blogging. I ended up a teary mess because I had no clue what to share! I have many interests and tons of knowledge however, it was hard for me to get it out of my brain and into social media.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Looking back, I know why. I hadn\'t defined my niche. I was trying to market to anyone and everyone who would come across my social media accounts. When I finally realized I had to niche it down, things began to come together and content creation became a breeze!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First things first. Who is your target audience? (Please don\'t say ANYONE who loves ____! This will only have you pulling out you hair and leave you frustrated and stuck in moving forward in building your brand.) What are their struggles? What solutions can you provide for them? What value can you offer them?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Next, once you know who you are marketing to, content is easy. Like, too easy, in my opinion. Let\'s use the example of health and wellness. My niche is women, 30+, who want to feel amazing in their skin, rock their self confidence, attain optimal and vibrant health and create a life that allows them more time with their families. So every time I create a piece of content, I am thinking about these women and how I can help them.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where do I find content? I keep my eyes open to topics that would be of interest to my niche. Seriously, health and wellness is a billion dollar industry and pretty much every where I go, there\'s information out there. When I\'m at the grocery store, checking out, I see&nbsp;magazine titles. When I\'m on Facebook, I see people posting about their issues. And one of my favorite places is the internet. I will google a few key words and boom! INSTANT IDEAS and CONTENT!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content creation isn\'t rocket science. It\'s being aware of the trends. It\'s knowing your audience. It\'s adding value with help, support and ideas. Remember, not everyone is in your niche. Not everyone is interested in what you have to offer. And that is 100% ok! Don\'t worry about them. Instead, start calling out your tribe and creating raving fans of your content,,then the sky\'s the limit on the impact you will make!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Receive my free gift - 8 Must Knows for Personal Branding&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/7secretssocialmediamakeover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">HERE</a>!</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Struggling to determine your personal brand? I know the feeling! After almost 2 years of studying and building my own brand, I offer one on one coaching. See if we\'re a good fit by filling out this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/H8MK97J\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>form</strong></a><a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></a>and I\'ll be in touch with you soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How I Stopped Struggling in My On Line Business', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '419-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-06 19:36:05', '2019-02-06 19:36:05', '', 419, 'http://handspeak.web-art.net/419-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
